    "The nextTable 4 Account classification ROC_AUC.",
    "Best results for each dataset are highlighted in darker shades Table 5 Account classification F1.",
    "Best results for each dataset are highlighted in darker shadesbest-performing algorithms are LoCred and Reputation Scaling; these algorithms consider reshares as information diffusion channels without assuming good judgment by accounts.",
    "TrustRank, Personalized PageRank Trust, and PageRank Trust, which assume that reshares capture trust and hence reputation, perform only marginally better than random at the task.",
